_sText:
The Courf Castle in Britain has been overrun by bandits of terrorists. They're now using the tour guides to the castle as hostages, and Counter-Terrorists quickly pick up the event. It's up to the CT's to breach the castle to save the hostages. Will they do it?

Nice things about this map:
-It can support up to 64 players
-Massive Castle Architecture to look at
-Good Framerates (up to 10v10)
-Dynamic elevation
-Parkour spots that you can get to
